This paper is about end-to-end speech recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers topics related to NLP and speech processing. The paper also discusses the use of high-performance computing (HPC) techniques, which could fall under cs.SD (Systems and Control) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses neural networks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
